50|$|The {{deamidation}} of <b>pyrazinamide</b> to pyrazinoic acid (assumed to be {{the active}} component of the drug <b>pyrazinamide)</b> in four days is a useful physiologic characteristic by which M. tuberculosis-complex members can be distinguished.|$|E
